    "Name": "Drillson CAV",
    "Details": "A licensed production variant built by Scarborough Manufacturers as a companion to their Maxim Mk II this variant upgrades the majority of the systems, the exceptions being the reliable Kicker machine guns. Scarborough elected to use surplus engines from the Maxim to reduce costs resulting in a top speed of 129 kph and a cruising speed of 86kph. It mounts 1 Large Pulse Laser, 2 Streak SRM-2s, 2 MML-5s, and 2 Machine Guns. It carries one ton of MML/LRM ammunition, one ton of MML/SRM ammunition, a half-ton of MG ammunition, and one ton of Streak SRM ammunition in CASE protected bins.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: None.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 9/14 hexes / 270/420 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       145     25\n<b>Left</b>         100     25\n<b>Right</b>       100     25\n<b>Rear</b>         90     25\n<b>Turret</b>      130     25\n\n<b>Total</b>      565    125</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Laser</color>",
